title: Weds Post Show (11-17-21)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (11-17-21)
description:
Bobby starts by being excited about the host on CBS for their New Year’s Eve special. Bobby also talks about his trainer working with Ryan Seacrest in Nashville. Bobby shares the Top 10 Netflix shows off all-time that they just relapsed the data for. Amy talks about the crazy process her friends had to go through to adopt a dog. We also get an update on Raymundo’s Trump Money and the wedding he went to in Mexico.
